 real, lasting results.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n<!-- wp:paragraph {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#374151\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.05rem\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"top\":\"1rem\"}}}} -->\r\n<p style=\"color:#374151;font-size:1.05rem;margin-top:1rem\">Our coaches are passionate, certified, and dedicated to your success. Every member gets a fully customized program built around their goals, schedule, and fitness level — with consistent coaching every step of the way.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- /wp:column -->\r\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"45%\"} -->\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-column\" style=\"flex-basis:45%\">\r\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":36,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img src=\"http://ep-fitness.local/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/2025-06-11-7-1.webp\" alt=\"EP Fitness coaching session\" class=\"wp-image-36\"/></figure>\r\n<!-- /wp:image -->\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- /wp:column -->\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- /wp:group -->\r\n\r\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#F3F4F6\"},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"clamp(4rem,8vw,7rem)\",\"bottom\":\"clamp(4rem,8vw,7rem)\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"constrained\"}} -->\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\" style=\"background-color:#F3F4F6;padding-top:clamp(4rem,8vw,7rem);padding-bottom:clamp(4rem,8vw,7rem)\">\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":6,\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#3B82F6\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"0.75rem\",\"fontWeight\":\"700\",\"textTransform\":\"uppercase\",\"letterSpacing\":\"0.15em\"},\"spacing\":{\"margin\":{\"bottom\":\"0.75rem\"}}}} -->\r\n<h6 class=\"wp-block-heading\" style=\"color:#3B82F6;font-size:0.75rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:0.75rem\">Meet The Team</h6>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":2,\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#0F172A\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"clamp(2rem,4vw