-text-color\" style=\"color:#374151;font-size:1rem\">Adults 40+ looking for real, lasting results. Beginners who want expert guidance from day one. Experienced athletes hitting a plateau. Anyone who wants a dedicated coach in their corner.</p>\r\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\r\n</div>\r\n<!-- /wp:column -->\r\n<!-- wp:column {\"width\":\"45%\"} -->\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:45%\">\r\n<!-- wp:heading {\"level\":4,\"style\":{\"color\":{\"text\":\"#0F172A\"},\"typography\":{\"fontSize\":\"1.25rem\",\"fontWeight\":\"700\"}}} -->\r\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-color\" style=\"color:#0F172A;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700\">WHAT\'S INCLUDED</h4>\r\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\r\n<!-- wp:list {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"left\":\"0\"}}},\"className\":\"ep-checklist\"} -->\r\n<ul class=\"ep-checklist\" style=\"padding-left:0\">\r\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n<li>Comprehensive body composition assessment</li>\r\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\r\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n<li>100% customized training program</li>\r\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\r\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n<li>Weekly check-ins with your coach</li>\r\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\r\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n<li>Nutrition guidance and meal planning support</li>\r\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\r\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n<li>Progress tracking and program adjustments</li>\r\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\r\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n<li>Flexible scheduling — morning, evening, weekends</li>\r\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\r\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\r\n<li>No contracts required</li>\r\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\r\n</ul>\r\n<!-- /wp:list -->\r\n<!-- wp:buttons {} -->\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\" style=\"\">\r\n<!-- wp:button {\"style\":{\"color\":{\"background\":\"#3B82F6\",\"text\":\"#FFFFFF\"},\"border\":{\"radius\":\"0px\"},\"typography\":{\"fontFamily\":\"var:preset|font-family|barlow-condensed\",\"fontWeight\":\"700\",\"textTr